feat: channels, scheduler, skills, WhatsApp reconnect fix - v1.0.4

Channels (new @vox-ai-app/channels package)
- WhatsApp via Baileys QR pairing
- Telegram via grammY
- Discord via discord.js
- Slack via Bolt
- Base adapter: EventEmitter, exponential backoff reconnect, message dedup, text chunking
- Fix WhatsApp disconnect race condition (abort before socket end, null controller guard)
- Full renderer UI: ChannelsPage, setup drawers, activity feed, thread viewer

Scheduler (new @vox-ai-app/scheduler package)
- Cron-based recurring/one-shot agentic tasks
- Persistent store with JSON file backend
- schedule_task, list_schedules, remove_schedule tool definitions
- Cron validation with minimum 5-min interval guard

Skills (new @vox-ai-app/skills package)
- SKILL.md frontmatter parser
- Directory-based skill loader with dedup and size limits
- XML prompt formatter injected into system prompt

App wiring
- channels.service, channels.ipc, channels.queue, channels.sessions
- skills.service integrated into chat.session system prompt
- scheduler.service with agent handler and graceful shutdown
- Drawer animation polish (opacity, box-shadow, content slide-in)
- Preload API for channels (list, init, disconnect, send, events)
- Left rail Channels tab with Radio icon

Tests: 528 passing across 21 files

Docs
- CHANGELOG [1.0.4] entry
- README beta features table
- Channels README with beta banner
